    <h3>District Information</h3>
    <p>With more than 20,000 students in the Blue Valley School District, "education beyond expectation" is the main goal and mission of its educators.  Enabling each and every student to realize their potential and become more than they ever thought or hoped to be is what every teacher strives for.  With a vision like this, it's easy to see that this district has been consistently ranked as one of the best school districts in the United States.  In addition to educating students to the highest degree, Blue Valley also tries to help positive relationships develop between the community and the schools, helping young minds grow and learn not just in the classroom, but in all aspects of their life.  The Blue Valley School District delivers one of the best educations available, and continues to try to grow and expand to lead the way in empowering the future of America.</p>
